caring /ˈkɛərɪŋ/

1. ADJ If someone is caring , they are affectionate, helpful, and sympathetic. 体贴的 

例： He is a lovely boy, very gentle and caring. 他是个可爱的男孩，既温柔又体贴。 

2. ADJ The caring professions are those such as nursing and social work that are involved with looking after people who are ill or who need help in coping with their lives. 护理的 [ADJ n] 

例： The course is also suitable for those in the caring professions. 这门课同样适合护理行业从业者。

